    colour map, the wrong number of NA's was sometimes produced.
    Fixed.

    o MinkowskiSum
    Crashed sometimes with an error message about 'sumconnected'.
    Fixed.

    o hyperframe
    Crashed if the argument 'row.names' was given
    and the hyperframe had exactly one row.
    Fixed.
    

